<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<div class="page-intro">
    <div class="eyebrow">Yoga Therapy</div>
    <h1>A whole-person approach to healing, balance, and embodied wellbeing.</h1>
    <p>
        I support women moving through grief, transition, pain, anxiety, and life's tender
        thresholds. Yoga therapy meets you exactly where you are.
    </p>
</div>

<section>
    <div class="container narrow">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="eyebrow">The Approach</span>
            <h2>What to expect</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
            My approach blends functional movement, breathwork, somatic awareness, nervous
            system regulation, and trauma-informed guidance to help you reconnect with your
            body, restore balance, and feel deeply supported.
        </p>
        <p>
            Whether you're navigating a major life change, living with chronic discomfort, or
            simply longing to feel more grounded and at home in yourself, each session is
            personalized to your lived experience—emotionally, physically, and energetically.
        </p>
        <p>Together, we may explore:</p>
        <ul class="soft-list">
            <li>Functional movement based on your unique limitations and strengths</li>
            <li>Breath practices to regulate your nervous system</li>
            <li>Somatic tools for grounding, emotional processing, and resilience</li>
            <li>Supportive dialogue that honors your story and lived history</li>
            <li>Gentle home practices to help you integrate change between sessions</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            This is not a workout. It is a healing relationship—one that centers safety,
            compassion, accountability, and empowered transformation.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-sage">
    <div class="container narrow">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="eyebrow">Is This for You?</span>
            <h2>Yoga therapy supports you through…</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="soft-list">
            <li>Grief, loss, or major life transitions</li>
            <li>Chronic pain or fatigue</li>
            <li>Anxiety, overwhelm, or dysregulation</li>
            <li>Joint discomfort</li>
            <li>Disconnection from your body or breath</li>
            <li>A desire to feel more grounded, clear, and resilient</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="text-align:center; margin-top:2rem;">If you're unsure where to begin, I'm happy to guide you.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="eyebrow">Sessions</span>
            <h2>The path forward</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">90 min</div>
                <h3>Initial Assessment</h3>
                <p>
                    A full evaluation of your movement, posture, breath, and nervous system
                    tendencies. We'll talk through your health history, symptoms, stressors,
                    and goals, and I'll send you home with personalized somatic and breath
                    practices.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">60 min</div>
                <h3>Follow-Up Sessions</h3>
                <p>
                    Progressive sessions that adapt to your needs week to week. Refinement of
                    your practices, nervous system support, pain management techniques, and
                    trauma-informed guidance.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">20 min</div>
                <h3>Mini Check-Ins</h3>
                <p>
                    Short virtual sessions for breath resets, emotional regulation support,
                    and real-time guidance during moments of overwhelm. A bridge between your
                    therapy sessions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="private" class="bg-cream">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
            <span class="eyebrow">Private Yoga</span>
            <h2>Deep Release · Deep Rest · Deep Connect</h2>
            <p style="max-width:640px; margin:1rem auto 0;">
                Intentionally curated private yoga practices that support well-being—focused
                on improving mobility, deepening rest, or cultivating mindful breathing.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">Yin</div>
                <h3>Deep Release</h3>
                <p>
                    Long-held floor poses to unwind deep tension and improve mobility.
                    Spacious, grounding, and deeply restorative for the fascia.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">Restore</div>
                <h3>Deep Rest</h3>
                <p>
                    Fully supported postures designed to calm the nervous system and invite
                    deep rest. A reset for an exhausted body and mind.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">Mindful</div>
                <h3>Deep Connect</h3>
                <p>
                    Guided breathwork and meditation to cultivate clarity, steadiness, and
                    emotional balance. Simple practices you can take with you.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="container narrow">
        <div class="pull-quote">
            "Healing occurs through consistency, compassion, and the practices we build
            together."
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/contact-block', {
    eyebrow: 'Ready to Begin?',
    heading: 'Book your first session.',
    body: 'Healing begins with one intentional step.'
}) %>

